    "\", the agent does not simply execute a predetermined sequence of commands.",
    "Instead, it exhibits the planning and tool-calling capabilities that define AI agents: it first thinks about what data would help answer the question, then acts by calling the appropriate external tool (the FRED API), observes by analyzing the returned data, and finally responds with a natural language answer.",
    "This Think-Act-Observe loop characterizes sophisticated agentic systems. 1.",
    "Understand a question ( Think) 2.",
    "Fetch economic data (Act) 3."
  ]
